Class BeamSqlFnExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.beam.sdk.extensions.sql.impl.interpreter.BeamSqlFnExecutor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, BeamSqlExpressionExecutor

    public class BeamSqlFnExecutor
extends java.lang.Object
implements BeamSqlExpressionExecutor
    Executor based on BeamSqlExpression and BeamSqlPrimitive. BeamSqlFnExecutor converts a BeamRelNode to a BeamSqlExpression, which can be evaluated against the BeamRecord.
